data.title: Johnny Wright (Music Manager)
data.meta_description: Listen to this episode from Frosted Tips with Lance Bass on Spotify. When it comes to music, Manager Johnny Wright has seen it all!  So who better to tell us the truth about the BSB/*NSYNC rivalry? Or *NSYNC’s rise to stardom... and first hand stories of Britney Spears!? This episode is an audio tell-all!  See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
